- throw_content :for_header, "Pending Screencasts"

.content_description
  %p
    These screencasts are waiting to be published by a person in the community that is a publisher.
  - unless current_person.publisher?
    %p
      You can become a publisher.  All you have to do is publish 5 items.  These could be either a Screencast or a Tutorial.
      Once your a publisher, you can publish your own, and anyone else's work that is pending approval.

- if @screencasts.empty?
  There are no Pending Screencasts.  Why not
  = link_to "make one", url(:new_screencast)
- else
  = partial :summary, :with => @screencasts, :as => "screencast"